About Vision Zero

  • Started in Swedish in October 1997

  • Adopted in January, 2014, announced by NYC Mayor Bill de Blasio

  • To reduce traffic fatalities

Major Initiatives

  • Legislative:
    • Speed Limit: 30 MPH -> 25 MPH
  • NYPD:
    • Stricter enforcement!
  • DOT:
    • More traffic signals
